      "retweeted_tweet_id": null,
      "text": "200,000+ lbs and counting!\n\nOperation Pacific Viper just hit a major milestone: over 200,000 pounds of narcotics interdicted across the Eastern Pacific. U.S. Coast Guard Cutter Seneca’s latest success – over 18,000 lbs of cocaine seized in one week – reflects sustained pressure on narco-terrorists.\n\nUsing every specialized capability at our disposal, the Coast Guard continues operations to control, secure, and defend U.S. borders and maritime approaches – where defense of America begins.\n\nWhen we say we’re accelerating counter-drug operations, we mean it.\n\nRead more at: https://t.co/C0cU9Bx1pi\n\n#USCG #DrugInterdiction #OperationPacificViper #WeOwnTheSea #EveryWarEveryShore @DHSgov @USCGPACAREA @USCGSouthwest @DeptofWar @Southcom @jiatfs",
      "text_resolved": "200,000+ lbs and counting!\n\nOperation Pacific Viper just hit a major milestone: over 200,000 pounds of narcotics interdicted across the Eastern Pacific. U.S. Coast Guard Cutter Seneca’s latest success – over 18,000 lbs of cocaine seized in one week – reflects sustained pressure on narco-terrorists.\n\nUsing every specialized capability at our disposal, the Coast Guard continues operations to control, secure, and defend U.S. borders and maritime approaches – where defense of America begins.\n\nWhen we say we’re accelerating counter-drug operations, we mean it.\n\nRead more at: https://tinyurl.com/36hyznmv\n\n#USCG #DrugInterdiction #OperationPacificViper #WeOwnTheSea #EveryWarEveryShore @DHSgov @USCGPACAREA @USCGSouthwest @DeptofWar @Southcom @jiatfs",
