      "text": "Defending America through Operation Pacific Viper.\nEarlier this week, the crew of Coast Guard Cutter Seneca interdicted a go-fast vessel NW of Ecuador following an airborne use-of-force stop by Coast Guard HITRON.\n\n✅ 3 suspected narco-terrorists apprehended. ✅ 4,400 lbs of cocaine seized. ✅ $33M+ in illicit drugs stopped at sea—before reaching our border.\n\nUnique authorities. Powerful capabilities. A safer nation.\n\n#USCG #DrugInterdiction #MaritimeSecurity #WeOwnTheSea @DHSgov @USCGLANTAREA",
